text: AHHHHHHHHHHHHHH!

Feeling hungry...

Welp, we're all out again.

We've got to be careful not to use up all our energy.
Be careful! This holds the experimental fluid that helps us grow.
type: Big tube that they are connected to

text: Don't need this anymore. They got us booster board workstations...so we could work on the way to the bathroom.
